structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.text: Proceedings under KRS 96.910 to 96.927 are purely discretionary. KRS 96.910 to 96.927 is not intended to be in derogation of any other law, and does not repeal or amend any other law.
law.history: Created 1958 Ky. Acts ch. 169, sec. 1, effective June 19, 1958.
